  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Passenger 23</strong> <strong>is a horror game centered around a student working at a rest stop.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your first shift is about to begin, and what awaits you is far more terrifying than you ever imagined. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/f455306f2c2f18034a1d114b7d6a9176.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/f455306f2c2f18034a1d114b7d6a9176.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Traces of the Past</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >23 passengers and a dark secret...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/61060f8d639d2e28c65ce9a2fb607cc1.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/61060f8d639d2e28c65ce9a2fb607cc1.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Midnight Visitor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The answers are dark, the questions even darker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/bebab1b62628db87064f13ded4414937.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/bebab1b62628db87064f13ded4414937.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your shift has started!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No matter what happens late into the night, you must keep making sales, keep the place clean, and continue selling tokens for passengers headed to the restroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/6732456840534fb033b1b31ece2ac10d.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/6732456840534fb033b1b31ece2ac10d.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Story:</strong> As tension and secrets escalate over time, a seemingly ordinary night shift turns into a deadly adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival and Exploration:</strong> Restore the power, uncover strange notes, and steer clear of the looming threats around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tense Atmosphere:</strong> Immerse yourself in an intense setting filled with darkness, solitude, and the eerie vibes of a rest stop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by a True Story:</strong> As the secrets of a 10-year-old accident come to light, you’ll face the dark side of justice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Graphics:</strong> Enjoy a nostalgic horror experience through PS1-style low-resolution aesthetics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Turkish and English Support:</strong> Experience the full depth of the story in both languages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
